```

---

## Create a Registry Value

```powershell
New-ItemProperty `
-Path HKLM:\Software\TestKey `
-Name Enabled `
-Value 1 `
-PropertyType DWord
```

---

## Modify a Registry Value

```powershell
Set-ItemProperty `
-Path HKLM:\Software\TestKey `
-Name Enabled `
-Value 0
```

---

## Delete a Registry Value

```powershell
Remove-ItemProperty `
-Path HKLM:\Software\TestKey `
-Name Enabled
```

---

## Delete a Registry Key

```powershell
Remove-Item HKLM:\Software\TestKey
```

---

## Export Registry

```cmd
reg export HKLM\Software C:\Software.reg
```

---

## Import Registry

```cmd
reg import C:\Software.reg
```

